      <h1>Engage Customers With User-Generated Content Campaigns</h1>
      <p class="lead">Discover how user-generated content (UGC) can enhance brand trust, loyalty, and community engagement. Start your UGC journey today!</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>August 2, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 25, 2025</span></p>
