      <details>
        <summary>What is user-generated content (UGC) in video marketing?</summary>
        <p>UGC is video content created by real customers sharing their own experiences with a product or brand, rather than content produced by the brand itself.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Why does UGC build more trust than traditional brand videos?</summary>
        <p>Because it shows real people using a product authentically, which builds social proof and makes a brand feel more relatable than polished, brand-produced advertising.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What are effective UGC campaign formats?</summary>
        <p>Customer challenges that invite people to share their stories, product use showcases in daily life, and community highlight reels that compile the best customer submissions.</p>
      </details>
      </div>
